def get_california_dataset():
    """Return the splits of the California housing dataset for training and testing"""
    X, y = fetch_california_housing(return_X_y=True)
    return train_test_split(X, y, random_state=42)

n_trees = np.floor(np.logspace(1, 3, num=10)).astype(int)

train_times = []
mae_train_values = []
mae_test_values = []

for n in n_trees:
    model = RandomForestRegressor(n_estimators=n, random_state=42)

    start_time = time.time()
    model.fit(X_train, y_train)
    elapsed_time = time.time() - start_time

    y_train_pred = model.predict(X_train)
    y_test_pred = model.predict(X_test)

    mae_train = mean_absolute_error(y_train, y_train_pred)
    mae_test = mean_absolute_error(y_test, y_test_pred)

    train_times.append(elapsed_time)
    mae_train_values.append(mae_train)
    mae_test_values.append(mae_test)

plt.figure(figsize=(12, 5))
plt.subplot(1, 2, 1)
plt.plot(n_trees, train_times, marker='o', linestyle='-', color='b', label=" ")
plt.xscale("log")
plt.xlabel(" ")
plt.ylabel(" ()")
plt.title("      ")
plt.legend()
plt.grid()

plt.subplot(1, 2, 2)
plt.plot(n_trees, mae_train_values, marker='o', linestyle='-', color='g', label="MAE   ")
plt.plot(n_trees, mae_test_values, marker='o', linestyle='-', color='r', label="MAE   ")
plt.xscale("log")
plt.xlabel(" ")
plt.ylabel("MAE")
plt.title("MAE     ")
plt.legend()
plt.grid()

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

In [36]:
def select_best_features(X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test, max_features=3):
    n_features = X_train.shape[1]
    remaining_features = list(range(n_features))
    selected_features = []

    for _ in range(max_features):
        best_feature = None
        best_mae = float("inf")

        for feature in remaining_features:
            temp_features = selected_features + [feature]
            model = DecisionTreeRegressor()
            model.fit(X_train[:, temp_features], y_train)
            y_pred = model.predict(X_test[:, temp_features])
            mae = mean_absolute_error(y_test, y_pred)

            if mae < best_mae:
                best_mae = mae
                best_feature = feature

        selected_features.append(best_feature)
        remaining_features.remove(best_feature)

    return selected_features
